    "# Loading Gradient Example\n",
    "networks  = list(index2region.keys())\n",
    "moviename = 'Sintel'\n",
    "tmp = load('./resources/dynamic_grad/individual_level/Sintel_40_grad.pkl')\n",
    "\n",
    "G_movie, varM = load('./resources/dynamic_grad/group_level/{}_40_grad.pkl'.format(moviename))\n",
    "# Loading Matching Emotion Track\n",
    "full_df  = pd.read_csv('./data/emoFiles/emotion_compile.csv')\n",
    "emo_df   = full_df[full_df['filename']=='W_{}13.csv'.format(moviename)]\n",
    "other_df = full_df[full_df['filename']!='W_{}13.csv'.format(moviename)]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "We would be interested in some examples found in notebook 7:\n",
    "- Sad/Dor/Metric 3\n",
    "- Anger/Dor/Metric 3"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 1. Compute sequence of network volume for group level\n",
    "\n",
    "geny  = np.asarray([network_volume(G_movie[t], networks[2]) \n",
    "                for t in range(len(G_movie))])\n",
    "geny = zscore(geny)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 2. Compute sequence of network volume for each individual\n",
    "subj_grads = np.asarray([tmp[s][0] for s in tmp])\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "subjects = list(tmp.keys())\n",
    "networks = list(index2region.keys())\n",
    "indiv_metrics = np.zeros((len(subjects), len(networks), subj_grads.shape[1]))\n",
    "for s in range(len(subjects)):\n",
    "    for n in range(len(networks)):\n",
    "        G_tmp = subj_grads[s]\n",
    "        y  = np.asarray([network_volume(G_tmp[t], networks[n]) \n",
    "                        for t in range(len(G_tmp))])\n",
    "        z1 = zscore(y)\n",
    "        indiv_metrics[s,n] = z1\n",
    "        # indiv_metric[s] = y / y.mean()  "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 20,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "emo_series = np.array(emo_df[emo_df.item=='Anger']['score'])\n",
    "smoothened = overlap_add(emo_series, 1)\n",
    "ye   = zscore(smoothened[:tmp.shape[0]])"
   ]
